---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - OSS Wishlist" description="Learn about project eligibility requirements and how the OSS Wishlist program works">
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About OSS Wishlist</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Connecting open source projects with the professional services they need to grow, scale, and thrive.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Overview Section -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          The OSS Wishlist program bridges the gap between open source maintainers and the professional services they need. 
          We connect projects with practitioner consultants who can provide governance setup, security audits, community building, 
          and other critical services that help projects succeed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Whether you're a maintainer looking for help or a service provider wanting to support the open source ecosystem, 
          OSS Wishlist creates meaningful connections that strengthen the entire community.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Project Requirements Section -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Project Eligibility Requirements</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          To ensure we can provide the most effective support, participating projects must meet the following criteria:
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Active User Base</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">At least 1,000 active downloads or demonstrated community engagement</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Independent Project</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Not already sponsored by a major foundation or corporation</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Good Community Standing</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Positive reputation and healthy relationships within your developer communities</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Process Commitment</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Willingness to participate in regular check-in meetings and program activities</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Feedback & Reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Commitment to provide feedback and participate in our annual impact survey</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- How It Works Section -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Submit Your Wishlist</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Tell us about your project and the services you need</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Get Matched</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">We connect you with qualified service providers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-600">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Grow Your Project</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Work with practitioners to strengthen and scale your project</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Service Providers Section -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">For Service Providers</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Are you a consultant, agency, or expert who wants to support the open source ecosystem? 
          We're looking for qualified professionals who can provide high-quality services to help projects succeed.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our network includes practitioners in governance, security, community building, developer relations, 
          and many other areas critical to project success.
        </p>
        <a href="/apply-practitioner" class="inline-block bg-gray-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
          Apply to Join Our Practitioner Network
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Get Started Section -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-lg border border-gray-300">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Ready to Get Started?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Browse our service catalog or submit your project's wishlist today
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/catalog" 
               class="bg-gray-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
              Browse Services
            </a>
            <a href="/maintainers" 
               class="bg-gray-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors">
              Submit Wishlist
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>